ok found a fix!

basically to use a type inside of Circuit we need to get rid of non-circuit-safe methods, we can infer a safe type as follows

```typescript
type RemoveMethods<T> = {
    [K in keyof T]: T[K] extends Function ? never : T[K];
};

type FilterNever<T> = {
    [K in keyof T as T[K] extends never ? never : K]: T[K];
};
```
then instead of
```typescript
const current_outcome: Outcome = Provable.if(
```
we do
```typescript
const current_outcome: FilterNever<RemoveMethods<Outcome>> = Provable.if(
```
( methods have been filtered and are no longer expected )
